Detection Ideas

Defenders should monitor for:

unusual LLMNR traffic
NBT-NS broadcasts for invalid names
rogue hosts responding to resolution requests
WPAD auth attempts to unexpected systems
SMB/HTTP auth to non-standard internal endpoints
